### Simulations

Math stuff in the browser.  View [here](dist/index.html)

The current GitHub pages build is from commit [d2fb3e: "initial commit"](https://github.com/pimlu/simulations/commit/d2fb3e0c0cd664867bb70db9069d92a78b5b9b1f).  If this is out of date, you can build it yourself- Emscripten is easy to use these days thanks to emsdk.
